Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveDolapo, the wife of the Vice President, Yemi Osinbajo, on Sunday, marked the Mother’s Day celebration with a throwback photo.
Mrs Osinbajo shared an old photo of herself with her mother and grandmother.
She captioned the image, “Happy Mother’s Day. God bless and keep all mothers and mothers-to-be. Amen.”
